    },
    {
      "time": 87.3,
      "time_str": "01:27.300",
      "text": "In the shade of night you're moving closer",
      "translation": "斑驳的夜色里你向我靠近"
    },
    {
      "time": 91.32,
      "time_str": "01:31.320",
      "text": "We're on our way to cross the line",
      "translation": "我们就快要越界"
    },
    {
